name: accuracy-assessment-plots-for-stones-river-national-battlefield-vegetation-mapping-project
notes: This is a vector file showing the location of NatureServe accuracy assessment sites at Stones River National Battlefield. The coordinates of this dataset were collected using Garmin GPS units.
